name: CABL MGMT
description:
This maze has been created during A Game By Its Cover 2022 jam as an homage to CABL MGMT, an entry to My Famicase exhibition, created by Arianna Dipollina.

Check out Arianna's entry here: https://famicase.com/22/softs/240.html

"a game where you finally get the chance to fight the naughty monster who has been tangling all your cables"

follow the cable carefully, it's easy to get tangled up! Can you get to the real end of the cable?

Made with bipsi  https://kool.tools/bipsi/
